1
00:00:00,590 --> 00:00:04,049
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

2
00:00:04,129 --> 00:00:05,565
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] There are just
two months left</b></Default>

3
00:00:05,589 --> 00:00:07,389
<Default><b>until the
Phoenix revives.</b></Default>

4
00:00:07,629 --> 00:00:08,905
<Default><b>In order to defeat it</b></Default>

5
00:00:08,929 --> 00:00:10,696
<Default><b>the four Heroes
are going to need to learn</b></Default>

6
00:00:10,720 --> 00:00:13,040
<Default><b>how to work together
as a team and fast.</b></Default>

7
00:00:15,310 --> 00:00:17,206
<Default><b>We also need
to fortify our defenses</b></Default>

8
00:00:17,230 --> 00:00:18,535
<Default><b>to protect the village.</b></Default>

9
00:00:18,559 --> 00:00:20,100
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

10
00:00:39,619 --> 00:00:42,146
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Hopefully, everyone's
ready when the time comes.</b></Default>

11
00:00:42,170 --> 00:00:44,880
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

12
00:00:45,000 --> 00:00:46,146
<Default><b>[both grunt]</b></Default>

13
00:00:46,170 --> 00:00:47,610
<Default><b>- [thudding]
- Hm.</b></Default>

14
00:00:47,759 --> 00:00:49,679
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

15
00:00:52,340 --> 00:00:54,060
<Default><b>Well, that should do it.</b></Default>

16
00:00:54,299 --> 00:00:56,219
<Default><b>- [stomach growling]
- [gasps]</b></Default>

17
00:00:56,770 --> 00:00:57,786
<Default><b>Looks delicious.</b></Default>

18
00:00:57,810 --> 00:00:59,076
<Default><b>The food'll
be ready soon</b></Default>

19
00:00:59,100 --> 00:01:01,220
<Default><b>so just wait
a little longer, okay?</b></Default>

20
00:01:01,899 --> 00:01:03,705
<Default><b>[KEEL] Aww, yeah!
I knew I smelled</b></Default>

21
00:01:03,729 --> 00:01:05,045
<Default><b>something
good over here!</b></Default>

22
00:01:05,069 --> 00:01:07,480
<Default><b>C'mon, you guys.
Hurry up, I'm starving!</b></Default>

23
00:01:08,319 --> 00:01:10,030
<Default><b>Hold up, is that Keel?</b></Default>

24
00:01:10,109 --> 00:01:12,530
<Default><b>- I think it is!
- [laughs]</b></Default>

25
00:01:12,659 --> 00:01:13,846
<Default><b>Pretty cool, huh?</b></Default>

26
00:01:13,870 --> 00:01:16,385
<Default><b>Sadeena's the one who taught me
how to turn into this.</b></Default>

27
00:01:16,409 --> 00:01:17,120
<Default><b>[Sadeena giggles]</b></Default>

28
00:01:17,239 --> 00:01:19,409
<Default><b>Well, Keel always
had the talent</b></Default>

29
00:01:19,540 --> 00:01:21,435
<Default><b>I just showed him
how to do it is all.</b></Default>

30
00:01:21,459 --> 00:01:23,605
<Default><b>And how does this affect
his abilities?</b></Default>

31
00:01:23,629 --> 00:01:25,646
<Default><b>Well, it typically depends
on the race</b></Default>

32
00:01:25,670 --> 00:01:27,146
<Default><b>but usually
they just get stronger.</b></Default>

33
00:01:27,170 --> 00:01:29,299
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

34
00:01:29,379 --> 00:01:30,656
<Default><b>[SADEENA]
By the way</b></Default>

35
00:01:30,680 --> 00:01:33,140
<Default><b>Fohl's capable
of transformation as well.</b></Default>

36
00:01:34,340 --> 00:01:36,469
<Default><b>[RISHIA]
Aw, look how cute Keel is!</b></Default>

37
00:01:36,599 --> 00:01:39,730
<Default><b>Hey! Cut it out, that tickles!
[laughs]</b></Default>

38
00:01:39,849 --> 00:01:42,036
<Default><b>- [RISHIA] You're so adorable!
- [KEEL] Stop!</b></Default>

39
00:01:42,060 --> 00:01:44,230
<Default><b>All right! Now
who's hungry?</b></Default>

40
00:01:44,349 --> 00:01:46,859
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

41
00:01:51,780 --> 00:01:53,715
<Default><b>Hey, Ren, come
here for a sec!</b></Default>

42
00:01:53,739 --> 00:01:55,139
<Default><b>Something wrong?</b></Default>

43
00:01:57,620 --> 00:01:59,079
<Default><b>What do you need?</b></Default>

44
00:01:59,579 --> 00:02:01,709
<Default><b>All yours. Give it a go.</b></Default>

45
00:02:02,750 --> 00:02:03,750
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

46
00:02:04,079 --> 00:02:05,119
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

47
00:02:05,459 --> 00:02:07,540
<Default><b>Instead of Sir Naofumi
serving us</b></Default>

48
00:02:07,629 --> 00:02:10,105
<Default><b>the Sword Hero will be
helping out for today.</b></Default>

49
00:02:10,129 --> 00:02:11,569
<Default><b>So gather 'round!</b></Default>

50
00:02:11,629 --> 00:02:14,590
<Default><b>Hurry up, Sword Hero!
We're starving!</b></Default>

51
00:02:14,719 --> 00:02:16,199
<Default><b>I'm getting to it!</b></Default>

52
00:02:16,300 --> 00:02:18,259
<Default><b>Uh, the food
is ready, right?</b></Default>

53
00:02:19,680 --> 00:02:21,640
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
I remember that girl.</b></Default>

54
00:02:22,889 --> 00:02:24,689
<Default><b>Her name is
Wyndia, right?</b></Default>

55
00:03:55,990 --> 00:03:58,949
<Default><b>[birds chirping]</b></Default>

56
00:04:01,240 --> 00:04:03,490
<Default><b>[FILO]
Master, get her off!</b></Default>

57
00:04:03,789 --> 00:04:05,830
<Default><b>Help me!</b></Default>

58
00:04:08,330 --> 00:04:10,145
<Default><b>[RAT]
Stop running away already!</b></Default>

59
00:04:10,169 --> 00:04:11,369
<Default><b>[both gasp]</b></Default>

60
00:04:11,669 --> 00:04:14,090
<Default><b>- [FILO] No!
- [both gasp]</b></Default>

61
00:04:14,629 --> 00:04:17,629
<Default><b>[screaming]</b></Default>

62
00:04:18,129 --> 00:04:21,009
<Default><b>Master, get her off me!</b></Default>

63
00:04:24,389 --> 00:04:25,889
<Default><b>[crying]</b></Default>

64
00:04:26,139 --> 00:04:27,639
<Default><b>- Filo!
- Huh.</b></Default>

65
00:04:27,769 --> 00:04:29,730
<Default><b>- Master, please help me.
- Hm.</b></Default>

66
00:04:29,810 --> 00:04:32,610
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

67
00:04:33,569 --> 00:04:35,049
<Default><b>Who is that, Filo?</b></Default>

68
00:04:35,319 --> 00:04:37,586
<Default><b>I don't know, she just
showed up out of nowhere</b></Default>

69
00:04:37,610 --> 00:04:39,216
<Default><b>and grabbed
onto my back.</b></Default>

70
00:04:39,240 --> 00:04:41,800
<Default><b>I'm guessing that you
must be the Shield Hero?</b></Default>

71
00:04:42,029 --> 00:04:43,079
<Default><b>Yeah.</b></Default>

72
00:04:43,240 --> 00:04:45,290
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

73
00:04:47,620 --> 00:04:49,620
<Default><b>My name is
Ratotille Anthreya.</b></Default>

74
00:04:49,920 --> 00:04:52,200
<Default><b>But all of my friends
just call me Rat.</b></Default>

75
00:04:52,379 --> 00:04:53,819
<Default><b>Nice to meet you.</b></Default>

76
00:04:55,170 --> 00:04:57,370
<Default><b>I can understand
why you're cautious.</b></Default>

77
00:05:00,800 --> 00:05:02,656
<Default><b>But I have a feeling
this might ease</b></Default>

78
00:05:02,680 --> 00:05:04,520
<Default><b>- your worries a bit.
- Huh.</b></Default>

79
00:05:05,720 --> 00:05:07,080
<Default><b>From the Queen?</b></Default>

80
00:05:08,810 --> 00:05:10,770
<Default><b>What's it say,
Master Naofumi?</b></Default>

81
00:05:11,310 --> 00:05:12,786
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] It says
that she's an alchemist</b></Default>

82
00:05:12,810 --> 00:05:15,410
<Default><b>who was exiled from Faubrey
for causing trouble</b></Default>

83
00:05:16,029 --> 00:05:18,045
<Default><b>but that she's also
more than talented enough</b></Default>

84
00:05:18,069 --> 00:05:20,989
<Default><b>to help my lands prosper
if I'm able to put her to use.</b></Default>

85
00:05:21,910 --> 00:05:24,386
<Default><b>There is one part of that
I'd like to correct.</b></Default>

86
00:05:24,410 --> 00:05:27,740
<Default><b>The only reason I was exiled
was because the idiots there</b></Default>

87
00:05:27,829 --> 00:05:29,886
<Default><b>refused to understand
my research.</b></Default>

88
00:05:29,910 --> 00:05:31,646
<Default><b>And what's
your specialty?</b></Default>

89
00:05:31,670 --> 00:05:33,230
<Default><b>I research monsters.</b></Default>

90
00:05:33,420 --> 00:05:36,540
<Default><b>My job is to alter their beings
and make them even stronger.</b></Default>

91
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:40,300
<Default><b>Well, it was my job before they
started spreading rumors</b></Default>

92
00:05:40,379 --> 00:05:42,589
<Default><b>about how I was a devil</b></Default>

93
00:05:42,680 --> 00:05:45,115
<Default><b>and then slaughtered
all of my research subjects!</b></Default>

94
00:05:45,139 --> 00:05:47,139
<Default><b>It was just
ghastly back there.</b></Default>

95
00:05:47,970 --> 00:05:49,530
<Default><b>- But...
- [whimpers]</b></Default>

96
00:05:50,350 --> 00:05:52,790
<Default><b>Maybe it was for the best
that it happened.</b></Default>

97
00:05:52,899 --> 00:05:55,360
<Default><b>After all, I have
a mutant filolial here</b></Default>

98
00:05:55,439 --> 00:05:57,439
<Default><b>that's capable of
human speech!</b></Default>

99
00:05:57,899 --> 00:06:00,610
<Default><b>[Filo screams]</b></Default>

100
00:06:00,740 --> 00:06:02,949
<Default><b>Melty! Help me!</b></Default>

101
00:06:03,029 --> 00:06:05,699
<Default><b>Aw, and there goes
my valuable test subject!</b></Default>

102
00:06:05,990 --> 00:06:07,470
<Default><b>Ratotille, was it?</b></Default>

103
00:06:08,160 --> 00:06:09,555
<Default><b>Just call me Rat.</b></Default>

104
00:06:09,579 --> 00:06:11,636
<Default><b>What is it that
you're after exactly?</b></Default>

105
00:06:11,660 --> 00:06:13,780
<Default><b>Well, if I were
to put it simply...</b></Default>

106
00:06:14,790 --> 00:06:16,070
<Default><b>The filolial.</b></Default>

107
00:06:16,379 --> 00:06:17,939
<Default><b>Wait, you mean Filo?</b></Default>

108
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:20,670
<Default><b>The Queen mentioned
in legends is one example.</b></Default>

109
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:23,379
<Default><b>That being said</b></Default>

110
00:06:23,550 --> 00:06:26,350
<Default><b>a great help to humanity
by taking us places.</b></Default>

111
00:06:26,509 --> 00:06:29,069
<Default><b>That's the kind of monster
I intend on making.</b></Default>

112
00:06:29,970 --> 00:06:32,519
<Default><b>Speaking of which</b></Default>

113
00:06:33,350 --> 00:06:36,086
<Default><b>If you don't mind, I'd love
to go and check it out.</b></Default>

114
00:06:36,110 --> 00:06:39,110
<Default><b>I'm quite curious to know
what you've raised as a Hero.</b></Default>

115
00:06:39,569 --> 00:06:40,649
<Default><b>Hmm?</b></Default>

116
00:06:41,360 --> 00:06:42,880
<Default><b>Should we show her?</b></Default>

117
00:06:44,069 --> 00:06:46,699
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Yeah.
I say we give her a chance.</b></Default>

118
00:06:47,779 --> 00:06:50,079
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

119
00:06:54,040 --> 00:06:56,040
<Default><b>Aw! My goodness.</b></Default>

120
00:06:56,379 --> 00:06:59,179
<Default><b>I've never seen a caterpilland
so big at this level.</b></Default>

121
00:07:00,629 --> 00:07:04,050
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
One, two, three? Wait.</b></Default>

122
00:07:04,470 --> 00:07:06,790
<Default><b>Yeah, I thought
we only had two of them.</b></Default>

123
00:07:07,050 --> 00:07:08,696
<Default><b>Where'd the
third come from?</b></Default>

124
00:07:08,720 --> 00:07:10,400
<Default><b>- [WYNDIA] No!
- [gasps]</b></Default>

125
00:07:10,430 --> 00:07:12,615
<Default><b>Come on you're not supposed
to be here!</b></Default>

126
00:07:12,639 --> 00:07:14,430
<Default><b>[gasps] There's two!</b></Default>

127
00:07:14,519 --> 00:07:15,995
<Default><b>There isn't a
third one, okay?</b></Default>

128
00:07:16,019 --> 00:07:17,915
<Default><b>Why is she
acting so strange?</b></Default>

129
00:07:17,939 --> 00:07:19,399
<Default><b>No clue. [Gasps]</b></Default>

130
00:07:22,610 --> 00:07:24,045
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA]
What is this?</b></Default>

131
00:07:24,069 --> 00:07:25,229
<Default><b>[all gasp]</b></Default>

132
00:07:26,660 --> 00:07:28,819
<Default><b>Master Naofumi,
look here!</b></Default>

133
00:07:30,660 --> 00:07:32,055
<Default><b>- [gasps]
- [chuckles]</b></Default>

134
00:07:32,079 --> 00:07:33,870
<Default><b>[kids gasp]</b></Default>

135
00:07:33,949 --> 00:07:35,266
<Default><b>[FOX EAR KID 07-A (F)]
I promise we'll take</b></Default>

136
00:07:35,290 --> 00:07:36,170
<Default><b>good care of them!</b></Default>

137
00:07:36,250 --> 00:07:38,079
<Default><b>Just please</b></Default>

138
00:07:38,170 --> 00:07:39,435
<Default><b>I'm sorry, you guys.</b></Default>

139
00:07:39,459 --> 00:07:41,065
<Default><b>But we really don't have
the resources</b></Default>

140
00:07:41,089 --> 00:07:42,226
<Default><b>to raise that many.</b></Default>

141
00:07:42,250 --> 00:07:44,250
<Default><b>I can take care of them
for you.</b></Default>

142
00:07:44,509 --> 00:07:45,670
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

143
00:07:45,800 --> 00:07:47,446
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] I guess
we do need a specialist</b></Default>

144
00:07:47,470 --> 00:07:49,590
<Default><b>who can make
our monsters stronger.</b></Default>

145
00:07:51,009 --> 00:07:52,049
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

146
00:07:52,680 --> 00:07:54,115
<Default><b>I don't like
being lied to.</b></Default>

147
00:07:54,139 --> 00:07:55,980
<Default><b>So unfortunately</b></Default>

148
00:07:56,060 --> 00:07:57,700
<Default><b>a slave crest from me.</b></Default>

149
00:07:58,019 --> 00:07:59,625
<Default><b>Is that all
right with you?</b></Default>

150
00:07:59,649 --> 00:08:02,230
<Default><b>Yes, anything
to do my research.</b></Default>

151
00:08:02,819 --> 00:08:04,699
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Then it's settled.</b></Default>

152
00:08:05,399 --> 00:08:07,740
<Default><b>Excellent.
I won't disappoint you.</b></Default>

153
00:08:08,240 --> 00:08:10,819
<Default><b>[WYNDIA]
Um, Mr. Shield Hero.</b></Default>

154
00:08:10,949 --> 00:08:11,829
<Default><b>- Huh?
- Huh?</b></Default>

155
00:08:11,910 --> 00:08:13,516
<Default><b>There's something else here
that I think</b></Default>

156
00:08:13,540 --> 00:08:15,740
<Default><b>you should see that
Siltvelt sent us.</b></Default>

157
00:08:16,459 --> 00:08:18,019
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA]
Siltvelt?</b></Default>

158
00:08:19,250 --> 00:08:21,890
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Whoa, what's that
big black egg there?</b></Default>

159
00:08:22,209 --> 00:08:23,726
<Default><b>Looks like a dragon egg.</b></Default>

160
00:08:23,750 --> 00:08:24,670
<Default><b>Is it really?</b></Default>

161
00:08:24,750 --> 00:08:26,950
<Default><b>I've always wanted
to raise a dragon!</b></Default>

162
00:08:27,220 --> 00:08:29,220
<Default><b>Filo won't be
happy about that.</b></Default>

163
00:08:29,509 --> 00:08:30,949
<Default><b>No, probably not.</b></Default>

164
00:08:31,680 --> 00:08:33,326
<Default><b>More powerful dragons
will breed</b></Default>

165
00:08:33,350 --> 00:08:35,076
<Default><b>with creatures
from any species</b></Default>

166
00:08:35,100 --> 00:08:36,456
<Default><b>which can
cause problems.</b></Default>

167
00:08:36,480 --> 00:08:38,826
<Default><b>They can easily destroy
a whole ecosystem.</b></Default>

168
00:08:38,850 --> 00:08:39,865
<Default><b>That's not true</b></Default>

169
00:08:39,889 --> 00:08:42,649
<Default><b>dragons are
strong and awesome</b></Default>

170
00:08:42,899 --> 00:08:45,659
<Default><b>I'm talking about the integrity
of ecosystems here!</b></Default>

171
00:08:45,899 --> 00:08:48,375
<Default><b>I can create something even
more powerful than a dragon</b></Default>

172
00:08:48,399 --> 00:08:50,279
<Default><b>as well if
you'd like me to.</b></Default>

173
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:52,120
<Default><b>Yeah, well</b></Default>

174
00:08:52,200 --> 00:08:55,005
<Default><b>it would be the strongest one
in the whole wide world!</b></Default>

175
00:08:55,029 --> 00:08:57,149
<Default><b>I guess we can try
raising it here.</b></Default>

176
00:08:57,409 --> 00:08:58,726
<Default><b>- [gasps]
- Rat, do you think</b></Default>

177
00:08:58,750 --> 00:08:59,936
<Default><b>you can handle it?</b></Default>

178
00:08:59,960 --> 00:09:02,669
<Default><b>Of course. Let's start
with a monster seal.</b></Default>

179
00:09:02,960 --> 00:09:04,226
<Default><b>Then there's
something else</b></Default>

180
00:09:04,250 --> 00:09:06,355
<Default><b>that I would like
your help with, Count.</b></Default>

181
00:09:06,379 --> 00:09:07,379
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

182
00:09:07,669 --> 00:09:10,509
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

183
00:09:10,759 --> 00:09:13,929
<Default><b>[chuckles] What the hell
are you doing with that, kid?</b></Default>

184
00:09:14,889 --> 00:09:17,449
<Default><b>Master Naofumi is trying
to keep the egg warm.</b></Default>

185
00:09:17,720 --> 00:09:18,956
<Default><b>We were told
that it's healthy</b></Default>

186
00:09:18,980 --> 00:09:20,916
<Default><b>for boosting
the dragon's stats.</b></Default>

187
00:09:20,940 --> 00:09:22,620
<Default><b>Why'd it have to be me?</b></Default>

188
00:09:23,519 --> 00:09:25,875
<Default><b>Ren, think you can you look
after this thing for me</b></Default>

189
00:09:25,899 --> 00:09:27,259
<Default><b>while I'm gone?</b></Default>

190
00:09:29,529 --> 00:09:32,070
<Default><b>I would, but due
to the curse series</b></Default>

191
00:09:32,200 --> 00:09:35,490
<Default><b>every single thing I touch
begins to rapidly degrade.</b></Default>

192
00:09:36,120 --> 00:09:39,500
<Default><b>- [gasps]
- No way! [Panting]</b></Default>

193
00:09:41,750 --> 00:09:43,105
<Default><b>- Huh.
- [WYNDIA] I refuse to let</b></Default>

194
00:09:43,129 --> 00:09:44,849
<Default><b>the Sword Hero touch it!</b></Default>

195
00:09:46,340 --> 00:09:49,060
<Default><b>[ELHART] [laughs] Guess you're
stuck with it then.</b></Default>

196
00:09:49,090 --> 00:09:51,340
<Default><b>[sighs] Can't Raphy
take care of it?</b></Default>

197
00:09:51,799 --> 00:09:54,549
<Default><b>What does Raphy know
about raising a dragon egg?</b></Default>

198
00:09:54,639 --> 00:09:56,399
<Default><b>- [sword thunks]
- [gasps]</b></Default>

199
00:09:56,600 --> 00:09:57,946
<Default><b>[ELHART] Here it is.</b></Default>

200
00:09:57,970 --> 00:10:00,889
<Default><b>This is the Siderite Katana
you asked for, Raphtalia.</b></Default>

201
00:10:05,360 --> 00:10:07,800
<Default><b>It's been a while
since I've made a katana.</b></Default>

202
00:10:07,980 --> 00:10:10,660
<Default><b>I guess I'm still not as good
as my teacher, huh?</b></Default>

203
00:10:10,899 --> 00:10:12,860
<Default><b>It's perfect.
May I hold it?</b></Default>

204
00:10:13,279 --> 00:10:14,479
<Default><b>Sure thing.</b></Default>

205
00:10:16,450 --> 00:10:17,890
<Default><b>I'm all finished.</b></Default>

206
00:10:18,120 --> 00:10:20,870
<Default><b>It's skill is called
Stardust Blade.</b></Default>

207
00:10:21,250 --> 00:10:23,970
<Default><b>It might be a skill kinda like
Ren's Meteor Slash.</b></Default>

208
00:10:24,289 --> 00:10:26,765
<Default><b>- We can try it out a bit later.
- Sounds good!</b></Default>

209
00:10:26,789 --> 00:10:28,789
<Default><b>Thank you
for your work, Elhart.</b></Default>

210
00:10:29,919 --> 00:10:31,235
<Default><b>I'm happy I could help.</b></Default>

211
00:10:31,259 --> 00:10:32,895
<Default><b>Now, is that all
you need for me?</b></Default>

212
00:10:32,919 --> 00:10:34,696
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
For now. We'll be back.</b></Default>

213
00:10:34,720 --> 00:10:36,920
<Default><b>Oh, as for that equipment
you gave me</b></Default>

214
00:10:37,100 --> 00:10:38,615
<Default><b>I'll let you know
when it's repaired.</b></Default>

215
00:10:38,639 --> 00:10:39,639
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

216
00:10:40,720 --> 00:10:41,769
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

217
00:10:42,850 --> 00:10:45,290
<Default><b>[chuckles] They certainly
don't waste time.</b></Default>

218
00:10:45,899 --> 00:10:48,899
<Default><b>[crickets chirping]</b></Default>

219
00:10:53,149 --> 00:10:54,429
<Default><b>[door creaks]</b></Default>

220
00:10:55,360 --> 00:10:56,370
<Default><b>Huh.</b></Default>

221
00:10:57,120 --> 00:10:58,505
<Default><b>[FOHL]
Having trouble sleeping?</b></Default>

222
00:10:58,529 --> 00:10:59,539
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

223
00:11:00,289 --> 00:11:01,830
<Default><b>[bed squeaking]</b></Default>

224
00:11:02,289 --> 00:11:04,009
<Default><b>Go and tuck yourself in.</b></Default>

225
00:11:05,210 --> 00:11:06,210
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

226
00:11:08,590 --> 00:11:11,460
<Default><b>Hey, brother</b></Default>

227
00:11:12,509 --> 00:11:13,829
<Default><b>Mom's lullaby?</b></Default>

228
00:11:14,340 --> 00:11:15,460
<Default><b>That one?</b></Default>

229
00:11:16,840 --> 00:11:18,040
<Default><b>[ATLA] Yes.</b></Default>

230
00:11:23,769 --> 00:11:26,980
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

231
00:11:59,179 --> 00:12:00,579
<Default><b>Goodnight, Atla.</b></Default>

232
00:12:00,929 --> 00:12:02,409
<Default><b>Have sweet dreams.</b></Default>

233
00:12:02,929 --> 00:12:04,809
<Default><b>I'll see you in
the morning.</b></Default>

234
00:12:09,809 --> 00:12:11,296
<Default><b>Goodnight, big brother.</b></Default>

235
00:12:11,320 --> 00:12:12,720
<Default><b>Pleasant dreams.</b></Default>

236
00:12:13,730 --> 00:12:14,890
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

237
00:12:21,740 --> 00:12:23,659
<Default><b>[birds chirping]</b></Default>

238
00:12:25,450 --> 00:12:26,490
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

239
00:12:26,789 --> 00:12:28,159
<Default><b>Really? Again?</b></Default>

240
00:12:29,250 --> 00:12:31,500
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

241
00:12:33,299 --> 00:12:35,840
<Default><b>Oh, good morning, Master.
How did you sleep?</b></Default>

242
00:12:35,919 --> 00:12:37,470
<Default><b>- [sighs]
- Hm.</b></Default>

243
00:12:38,009 --> 00:12:40,025
<Default><b>How many times
have you done this?</b></Default>

244
00:12:40,049 --> 00:12:42,969
<Default><b>I think it's the third time
I've shared a bed with you.</b></Default>

245
00:12:43,100 --> 00:12:45,100
<Default><b>I mean, wandered
into your bed.</b></Default>

246
00:12:45,679 --> 00:12:48,389
<Default><b>Yeah, I'm sure.
How's your slave crest?</b></Default>

247
00:12:48,690 --> 00:12:51,290
<Default><b>My heart feels more warmth
than pain right now.</b></Default>

248
00:12:51,360 --> 00:12:53,836
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Why isn't Fohl
keeping watch over you?</b></Default>

249
00:12:53,860 --> 00:12:56,990
<Default><b>At the moment, he's most likely
sound asleep in his room.</b></Default>

250
00:12:57,070 --> 00:12:58,700
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

251
00:12:59,700 --> 00:13:01,620
<Default><b>Master Naofumi!
Good morning.</b></Default>

252
00:13:02,990 --> 00:13:04,620
<Default><b>Really, Atla, again?</b></Default>

253
00:13:04,870 --> 00:13:06,150
<Default><b>Good morning.</b></Default>

254
00:13:06,539 --> 00:13:08,806
<Default><b>You're not welcome
to sleep in this room.</b></Default>

255
00:13:08,830 --> 00:13:11,186
<Default><b>How many times
do you have to be told that?</b></Default>

256
00:13:11,210 --> 00:13:13,379
<Default><b>But I am
Master Naofumi's shield.</b></Default>

257
00:13:13,669 --> 00:13:16,629
<Default><b>I need to be by his side</b></Default>

258
00:13:17,009 --> 00:13:19,129
<Default><b>If you're his shield</b></Default>

259
00:13:19,220 --> 00:13:21,840
<Default><b>and stay in your own bed</b></Default>

260
00:13:21,929 --> 00:13:24,639
<Default><b>It's up to Master Naofumi
if I'm disturbing him.</b></Default>

261
00:13:24,720 --> 00:13:26,059
<Default><b>[FOHL] Atla!</b></Default>

262
00:13:26,389 --> 00:13:28,956
<Default><b>I'm pretty sure I told you
not to come over here.</b></Default>

263
00:13:28,980 --> 00:13:31,035
<Default><b>- So then why did you...
- Don't tell me what to do!</b></Default>

264
00:13:31,059 --> 00:13:32,099
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

265
00:13:32,559 --> 00:13:33,649
<Default><b>[thuds]</b></Default>

266
00:13:34,980 --> 00:13:37,820
<Default><b>Enough, Atla, it's time
for you to go back now!</b></Default>

267
00:13:38,190 --> 00:13:39,990
<Default><b>But I don't wanna!
[grunts]</b></Default>

268
00:13:40,450 --> 00:13:43,700
<Default><b>[gasps] Can't I just stay
with him a little longer?</b></Default>

269
00:13:44,950 --> 00:13:45,990
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

270
00:13:46,029 --> 00:13:47,240
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

271
00:13:50,659 --> 00:13:51,710
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

272
00:13:52,080 --> 00:13:54,880
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] That was a hell
of a way to start the day.</b></Default>

273
00:13:55,710 --> 00:13:58,710
<Default><b>[birds chirping]</b></Default>

274
00:14:03,549 --> 00:14:06,049
<Default><b>- [giggling]
- Hm? Huh.</b></Default>

275
00:14:07,679 --> 00:14:09,730
<Default><b>Hm. What is it?</b></Default>

276
00:14:10,639 --> 00:14:13,119
<Default><b>You're looking great
with that egg, Naofumi!</b></Default>

277
00:14:13,190 --> 00:14:16,030
<Default><b>Who knew you'd be a great cook
and a great caretaker?</b></Default>

278
00:14:16,440 --> 00:14:18,916
<Default><b>I'll bet you'd make
a wonderful dad someday.</b></Default>

279
00:14:18,940 --> 00:14:21,860
<Default><b>You're interrupting my work.
Get lost you two.</b></Default>

280
00:14:21,990 --> 00:14:24,255
<Default><b>[MELTY] Hey, I've got
a busy schedule, too</b></Default>

281
00:14:24,279 --> 00:14:26,505
<Default><b>and I still made time
to come see you!</b></Default>

282
00:14:26,529 --> 00:14:28,209
<Default><b>- [door opens]
- [gasps]</b></Default>

283
00:14:28,740 --> 00:14:31,515
<Default><b>[DOLL] Hi, Sir Naofumi.
I hope I'm not interrupting.</b></Default>

284
00:14:31,539 --> 00:14:33,686
<Default><b>Hey, that stuffed animal
looks like me!</b></Default>

285
00:14:33,710 --> 00:14:36,210
<Default><b>- Wow, it's so cute!
- Thank you!</b></Default>

286
00:14:36,460 --> 00:14:39,260
<Default><b>I based it off of how Keel
looks when he transforms.</b></Default>

287
00:14:39,590 --> 00:14:42,510
<Default><b>Wow, you're a whole lot easier
to understand with that.</b></Default>

288
00:14:42,840 --> 00:14:44,775
<Default><b>The reason is
I was able to...</b></Default>

289
00:14:44,799 --> 00:14:46,405
<Default><b>I was able
to repair an accessory</b></Default>

290
00:14:46,429 --> 00:14:48,535
<Default><b>that one of the enemies
we defeated had.</b></Default>

291
00:14:48,559 --> 00:14:51,039
<Default><b>It has a translation ability
that I can use.</b></Default>

292
00:14:51,519 --> 00:14:53,826
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
You can't just use it yourself?</b></Default>

293
00:14:53,850 --> 00:14:54,890
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

294
00:14:55,309 --> 00:14:57,535
<Default><b>[DOLL] It reacts poorly
with my vassal weapon.</b></Default>

295
00:14:57,559 --> 00:14:59,039
<Default><b>So I am unable to.</b></Default>

296
00:14:59,610 --> 00:15:00,770
<Default><b>Ah, I see.</b></Default>

297
00:15:01,279 --> 00:15:03,039
<Default><b>So, what
brings you here?</b></Default>

298
00:15:03,190 --> 00:15:05,110
<Default><b>- [stomach growling]
- [gasps]</b></Default>

299
00:15:05,279 --> 00:15:07,199
<Default><b>We should
probably eat first.</b></Default>

300
00:15:07,409 --> 00:15:08,569
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

301
00:15:09,539 --> 00:15:11,289
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

302
00:15:14,870 --> 00:15:15,870
<Default><b>Hmm.</b></Default>

303
00:15:16,789 --> 00:15:18,476
<Default><b>[ECLAIR]
Melromarc's language, huh?</b></Default>

304
00:15:18,500 --> 00:15:19,540
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

305
00:15:19,710 --> 00:15:20,870
<Default><b>Let's see.</b></Default>

306
00:15:22,340 --> 00:15:25,759
<Default><b>The spelling here</b></Default>

307
00:15:27,470 --> 00:15:29,049
<Default><b>[scribbling]</b></Default>

308
00:15:29,720 --> 00:15:30,760
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

309
00:15:31,220 --> 00:15:32,220
<Default><b>Hm?</b></Default>

310
00:15:32,389 --> 00:15:34,480
<Default><b>- What's wrong?
- It's nothing.</b></Default>

311
00:15:37,190 --> 00:15:39,206
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA] Thanks
for cooking this morning.</b></Default>

312
00:15:39,230 --> 00:15:41,836
<Default><b>We're getting more
and more therianthropes, huh.</b></Default>

313
00:15:41,860 --> 00:15:44,836
<Default><b>Yeah, we'll have to come up
with something for them, too.</b></Default>

314
00:15:44,860 --> 00:15:47,540
<Default><b>Well, what if we went
and got a new pot for them?</b></Default>

315
00:15:48,070 --> 00:15:50,350
<Default><b>I saw a store in Zeltoble
that had one.</b></Default>

316
00:15:50,830 --> 00:15:51,870
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

317
00:15:52,990 --> 00:15:54,306
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA]
When did that...</b></Default>

318
00:15:54,330 --> 00:15:56,710
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

319
00:15:56,830 --> 00:15:59,840
<Default><b>[hammering]</b></Default>

320
00:16:01,039 --> 00:16:02,395
<Default><b>- [NAOFUMI] Rat!
- Hm?</b></Default>

321
00:16:02,419 --> 00:16:04,099
<Default><b>Is it finished already?</b></Default>

322
00:16:04,419 --> 00:16:06,859
<Default><b>Yes, I've been here
waiting for you, Count!</b></Default>

323
00:16:08,129 --> 00:16:10,609
<Default><b>These giant trees
are called camping plants.</b></Default>

324
00:16:11,350 --> 00:16:13,115
<Default><b>Just plant the seed
and before long</b></Default>

325
00:16:13,139 --> 00:16:15,379
<Default><b>you'll have
a brand new place to live!</b></Default>

326
00:16:15,809 --> 00:16:17,245
<Default><b>It stores sunlight
during the day</b></Default>

327
00:16:17,269 --> 00:16:19,399
<Default><b>and when night comes</b></Default>

328
00:16:19,519 --> 00:16:20,916
<Default><b>That's real impressive.</b></Default>

329
00:16:20,940 --> 00:16:22,100
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

330
00:16:22,570 --> 00:16:24,570
<Default><b>- What's wrong?
- Nothing.</b></Default>

331
00:16:25,110 --> 00:16:26,926
<Default><b>It just feels like
we're getting</b></Default>

332
00:16:26,950 --> 00:16:28,755
<Default><b>further and further away
from the village</b></Default>

333
00:16:28,779 --> 00:16:30,179
<Default><b>I know and love.</b></Default>

334
00:16:30,700 --> 00:16:32,635
<Default><b>Well, I've got plenty
of weed killer to remove it</b></Default>

335
00:16:32,659 --> 00:16:34,219
<Default><b>if you'd like me to.</b></Default>

336
00:16:34,409 --> 00:16:36,476
<Default><b>If it makes life easier
for people in the village</b></Default>

337
00:16:36,500 --> 00:16:38,140
<Default><b>then I'm okay with it.</b></Default>

338
00:16:38,370 --> 00:16:40,290
<Default><b>- [egg crackling]
- [all gasp]</b></Default>

339
00:16:41,629 --> 00:16:42,829
<Default><b>It cracked!</b></Default>

340
00:16:43,669 --> 00:16:46,590
<Default><b>- [wind whooshing]
- [birds chirping]</b></Default>

341
00:16:47,049 --> 00:16:50,049
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

342
00:16:51,429 --> 00:16:52,720
<Default><b>Oh, good</b></Default>

343
00:16:52,799 --> 00:16:55,259
<Default><b>Hey, what exactly do
dragons eat anyway?</b></Default>

344
00:16:55,350 --> 00:16:57,670
<Default><b>Dragons eat just about
anything, really.</b></Default>

345
00:16:57,809 --> 00:17:00,100
<Default><b>- They are omnivores.
- [crackling]</b></Default>

346
00:17:00,350 --> 00:17:01,390
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

347
00:17:01,649 --> 00:17:02,940
<Default><b>[all gasp]</b></Default>

348
00:17:05,109 --> 00:17:06,269
<Default><b>[chirping]</b></Default>

349
00:17:06,900 --> 00:17:09,660
<Default><b>Well, I can't say this is
quite what I had in mind.</b></Default>

350
00:17:09,700 --> 00:17:11,620
<Default><b>I can't believe
it's so cute.</b></Default>

351
00:17:11,700 --> 00:17:14,660
<Default><b>It reminds me of back when
Filo was just a little chick.</b></Default>

352
00:17:14,740 --> 00:17:16,345
<Default><b>- [Naofumi gasps]
- Well then.</b></Default>

353
00:17:16,369 --> 00:17:18,476
<Default><b>Looks like a healthy
dragon pup to me.</b></Default>

354
00:17:18,500 --> 00:17:20,500
<Default><b>- Hmm.
- And a male one at that.</b></Default>

355
00:17:21,250 --> 00:17:23,010
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
What kind is it?</b></Default>

356
00:17:23,170 --> 00:17:24,436
<Default><b>A wyr, I think.</b></Default>

357
00:17:24,460 --> 00:17:25,515
<Default><b>And luckily for you</b></Default>

358
00:17:25,539 --> 00:17:28,139
<Default><b>they're one of the most loyal
types of dragons.</b></Default>

359
00:17:28,299 --> 00:17:29,499
<Default><b>[both gasp]</b></Default>

360
00:17:30,589 --> 00:17:32,220
<Default><b>- Hmm.
- [chirping]</b></Default>

361
00:17:32,299 --> 00:17:36,640
<Default><b>From here on out</b></Default>

362
00:17:37,430 --> 00:17:39,430
<Default><b>Yeah, your
name's Gaelion!</b></Default>

363
00:17:39,599 --> 00:17:40,809
<Default><b>[chirping]</b></Default>

364
00:17:41,190 --> 00:17:43,559
<Default><b>You like that, don't you?
[chuckles]</b></Default>

365
00:17:44,059 --> 00:17:46,585
<Default><b>Are you sure you don't want
to name the dragon yourself?</b></Default>

366
00:17:46,609 --> 00:17:48,716
<Default><b>He seems to have taken
a liking to that name</b></Default>

367
00:17:48,740 --> 00:17:50,340
<Default><b>so it's fine with me.</b></Default>

368
00:17:50,740 --> 00:17:53,140
<Default><b>Wyndia, since you're
the one who named him</b></Default>

369
00:17:53,200 --> 00:17:55,136
<Default><b>it's up to you
to take care of him.</b></Default>

370
00:17:55,160 --> 00:17:56,160
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

371
00:17:56,279 --> 00:17:58,539
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

372
00:19:13,650 --> 00:19:15,450
<Default><b>- [knocking on door]
- Huh?</b></Default>

373
00:19:15,490 --> 00:19:17,090
<Default><b>- [thudding]
- [gasps]</b></Default>

374
00:19:19,700 --> 00:19:22,000
<Default><b>What's going
on over here</b></Default>

375
00:19:24,039 --> 00:19:26,710
<Default><b>All right</b></Default>

376
00:19:30,539 --> 00:19:32,219
<Default><b>Wait, you triggered it?</b></Default>

377
00:19:32,880 --> 00:19:34,400
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA]
Gaelion?</b></Default>

378
00:19:36,089 --> 00:19:37,809
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Where's Wyndia?</b></Default>

379
00:19:39,509 --> 00:19:41,285
<Default><b>Somebody's been
knocking on my door</b></Default>

380
00:19:41,309 --> 00:19:43,575
<Default><b>and then running away
for the past few days</b></Default>

381
00:19:43,599 --> 00:19:45,119
<Default><b>so I set up a trap.</b></Default>

382
00:19:45,309 --> 00:19:47,309
<Default><b>Turns out it was
him all along.</b></Default>

383
00:19:47,730 --> 00:19:50,190
<Default><b>Why Gaelion?</b></Default>

384
00:19:51,440 --> 00:19:54,609
<Default><b>He says that he just wanted
to play with the Shield Hero.</b></Default>

385
00:19:56,069 --> 00:19:58,005
<Default><b>So you were just
playing a prank on me</b></Default>

386
00:19:58,029 --> 00:20:00,029
<Default><b>'cause I wouldn't
play with you?</b></Default>

387
00:20:00,450 --> 00:20:03,619
<Default><b>I know! This might be
a perfect opportunity for us!</b></Default>

388
00:20:03,700 --> 00:20:04,700
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

389
00:20:05,160 --> 00:20:07,055
<Default><b>He could certainly help
with Atla.</b></Default>

390
00:20:07,079 --> 00:20:08,805
<Default><b>We could have him stationed
outside the door</b></Default>

391
00:20:08,829 --> 00:20:11,356
<Default><b>to drive her off, so that she
doesn't wander in here.</b></Default>

392
00:20:11,380 --> 00:20:13,130
<Default><b>- [squeaking]
- [gasps]</b></Default>

393
00:20:13,460 --> 00:20:16,380
<Default><b>- [gasps]
- [squeaking]</b></Default>

394
00:20:19,009 --> 00:20:21,089
<Default><b>So, he'd be like
a guard dog, huh?</b></Default>

395
00:20:26,809 --> 00:20:28,730
<Default><b>What is that? An orb?</b></Default>

396
00:20:29,099 --> 00:20:30,339
<Default><b>It's a core.</b></Default>

397
00:20:30,599 --> 00:20:31,876
<Default><b>The Emperor
Dragon's Core.</b></Default>

398
00:20:31,900 --> 00:20:34,780
<Default><b>I had them turn into a jewel
for me in Kizuna's world.</b></Default>

399
00:20:35,569 --> 00:20:36,666
<Default><b>[both gasp]</b></Default>

400
00:20:36,690 --> 00:20:39,255
<Default><b>[SADEENA] Stop! Get that away
from him, quickly!</b></Default>

401
00:20:39,279 --> 00:20:41,619
<Default><b>[squeaking]</b></Default>

402
00:20:42,279 --> 00:20:44,450
<Default><b>Gaelion! Spit
it out already!</b></Default>

403
00:20:45,079 --> 00:20:46,410
<Default><b>[whimpering]</b></Default>

404
00:20:46,660 --> 00:20:48,305
<Default><b>Quick, Raphtalia, water!</b></Default>

405
00:20:48,329 --> 00:20:49,649
<Default><b>- Huh.
- Right!</b></Default>

406
00:20:50,750 --> 00:20:52,420
<Default><b>Gaelion, are you okay?</b></Default>

407
00:20:52,960 --> 00:20:54,440
<Default><b>Hurry, stand back!</b></Default>

408
00:20:57,920 --> 00:20:58,985
<Default><b>What happened?</b></Default>

409
00:20:59,009 --> 00:21:00,929
<Default><b>What's going
on with Gaelion?</b></Default>

410
00:21:02,339 --> 00:21:03,499
<Default><b>[growling]</b></Default>

411
00:21:04,140 --> 00:21:05,906
<Default><b>- [WYNDIA] Gaelion?
- [fire roaring]</b></Default>

412
00:21:05,930 --> 00:21:07,890
<Default><b>- [Naofumi gasps]
- [explosion]</b></Default>

413
00:21:08,099 --> 00:21:09,739
<Default><b>- [gasps]
- [both gasp]</b></Default>

414
00:21:10,019 --> 00:21:12,150
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

415
00:21:15,069 --> 00:21:16,859
<Default><b>- Damn it!
- This is bad.</b></Default>

416
00:21:17,029 --> 00:21:19,626
<Default><b>We need to deal with him
before he harms the village.</b></Default>

417
00:21:19,650 --> 00:21:21,886
<Default><b>Just tell me how we can
save him and I'm on it!</b></Default>

418
00:21:21,910 --> 00:21:24,200
<Default><b>- Please! Gaelion!
- [fire roaring]</b></Default>

419
00:21:24,990 --> 00:21:26,789
<Default><b>[growling]</b></Default>

420
00:21:29,460 --> 00:21:30,660
<Default><b>[roaring]</b></Default>

421
00:21:32,460 --> 00:21:34,170
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

422
00:21:37,009 --> 00:21:38,920
<Default><b>[fluttering]</b></Default>

423
00:21:39,380 --> 00:21:40,630
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

424
00:21:42,180 --> 00:21:43,390
<Default><b>[swooshing]</b></Default>

425
00:21:45,099 --> 00:21:46,180
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

426
00:21:46,349 --> 00:21:47,809
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

427
00:21:52,480 --> 00:21:53,840
<Default><b>[Naofumi gasps]</b></Default>

428
00:21:55,900 --> 00:21:57,029
<Default><b>Gaelion.</b></Default>

429
00:21:57,279 --> 00:21:59,029
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

